{
  "stem": "15197.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were all those day after day, and we have also to be involved in it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And little by little when people with special Jews were coming home and beaten up and when things were being taken away, when all those swear that Jews have to give the fur coat and Jews has to give the jewelry and Jews has to give up their factories and materials and things, so we start feeling and the fear was growing from day to day.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is going to be tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What new order?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jews are not permitted to go on trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jew are not permitted to go into pubs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jew are not permitted to have stalls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this, the fear was growing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was, I would say, the main atmosphere among Jews, that somehow we are separated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And special when we start having our armbands, we were even more afraid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were singled out and right away recognized that we are different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How did the Polish population change when these anti-Jewish laws became--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish population didn't change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polish population was taking this-- of course the Jews were different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are lower than the Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would not say that they sympathize that we are singled out for the negative way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not a big change for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a half an hour?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
